SubjectExchange of Notes amending the Agreement for the Establishment of a Binational Educational Exchange Foundation (Canada-United States)
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the action necessary to bring into force for Canada the EXCHANGE OF NOTES amending the Agreement between the Government of Canada and the Government of the United States of America for the Establishment of a Binational Educational Exchange Foundation (the CANADA-U.S. FULBRIGHT PROGRAM), done at Washington, on November 15, 1999.
